  "texts": [
    "Huls et al. (2022) report on a validation study of an attitude measurement instrument, the Health-Risk Attitude Scale (HRAS-13).",
    "This measurement instrument contains items such as \"my health means everything to me\", \"people say that I take risks with my health because of my habits\", and \"I think that I take good care of my body\".",
    "These items have to be rated on a sevenpoint response scale ranging from \"completely disagree\" to \"completely agree.\"",
    "Taylor et al. (2022) report on a mixed method study where interviews were used to delve deeper into mothers' attitudes regarding HPV vaccination.",
    "They describe that \"[...] all of the mothers attended screening because of its considered importance, with several expressing the opinion that it is something they had to do [...]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Huls et al. (2022) report on a validation study of an attitude measurement instrument, the Health-Risk Attitude Scale (HRAS-13).",
    "Taylor et al. (2022) report on a mixed method study where interviews were used to delve deeper into mothers' attitudes regarding HPV vaccination."
  ]
